ef=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/requestSubmit\"><code>requestSubmit()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/reset\"><code>reset()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/submit\"><code>submit()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/formdata_event\"><code>formdata</code></a></li><li><em><code>reset</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/submit_event\"><code>submit</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>The <code><strong>GlobalEventHandlers.onreset</strong></code>&nbsp;属性包含&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> ，当收到一个<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/reset_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">reset (en-US)</a></code> 事件时触发</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">window.onreset = funcRef;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>funcRef</code> 是一个函数的引用。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">&lt;html&gt;\n&lt;script&gt;\nfunction reg() {\n  window.captureEvents(Event.RESET);\n  window.onreset = hit;\n}\n\nfunction hit() {\n alert('hit');\n}\n&lt;/script&gt;\n\n&lt;body onload=\"reg();\"&gt;\n &lt;form&gt;\n   &lt;input type=\"reset\" value=\"reset\" /&gt;\n &lt;/form&gt;\n &lt;div id=\"d\"&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"备注","isH3":false,"content":"<p>reset 事件只有在用户点击表单中的 reset 按钮时才会被触发&nbsp;(<code>&lt;input type=\"reset\"/&gt;</code>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spectable standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">评论</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#handler-onreset\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">onreset</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例子","id":"example"},{"text":"备注","id":"notes"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"}],"summary":"The GlobalEventHandlers.onreset 属性包含 event handler ，当收到一个reset (en-US) 事件时触发","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"window.onreset","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/htmlformelement/reset_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/htmlformelement/reset_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API","title":"指数"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/reset_event","title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onreset"}],"pageTitle":"GlobalEventHandlers.onreset | MDN","noIndexing":true}}